# Part 2 — Describe an important decision you made in life.

One of the most important decisions I’ve ever made was deciding to focus seriously on artificial intelligence and computer science as my long-term career direction. I made this decision during my university years, especially after I started learning programming and realized how powerful technology could be in solving real-world problems.

At first, I was actually quite uncertain about my future. Like many students, I considered several possible career paths, and I wasn’t completely confident about what I truly wanted to do. However, after taking some computer science courses and trying algorithm problems and AI-related projects, I gradually became fascinated by the field. I was especially inspired by how AI can influence areas like robotics, healthcare and education.

I didn’t make the decision impulsively. I spent a lot of time thinking carefully about my strengths, interests and long-term goals. I also watched lectures from famous researchers, read about successful AI scientists, and talked with seniors who were already working in the tech industry. Eventually, I realized that this was not only something I was good at, but also something I genuinely enjoyed spending hours on every day.

This decision was extremely important to me because it completely changed my mindset and gave me a clear sense of direction. After making that choice, I became much more disciplined and motivated. I started preparing seriously for my future, improving my English, practicing coding regularly and learning machine learning step by step. I think having a clear goal makes people more confident and resilient, especially when facing difficulties.

Looking back, I believe this decision shaped not only my academic path, but also the person I want to become in the future.

---

### 中文翻译：

我人生中做过最重要的决定之一，就是决定认真把人工智能和计算机科学作为我长期发展的职业方向。我是在大学期间做出这个决定的，尤其是在开始学习编程之后，我意识到科技在解决现实问题方面有多么强大。

一开始，其实我对未来是比较迷茫的。像很多学生一样，我考虑过不同的发展方向，也并不完全确定自己真正想做什么。然而，在学习了一些计算机课程、刷算法题以及尝试AI项目之后，我逐渐对这个领域产生了浓厚兴趣。我尤其被人工智能在机器人、医疗和教育等领域的影响力所吸引。

我并不是冲动地做出这个决定的。我花了很多时间认真思考自己的优势、兴趣以及长期目标。我还观看了很多知名研究者的演讲，阅读优秀AI科学家的经历，并且和一些已经进入科技行业的学长交流。最后我意识到，这不仅是我擅长的领域，也是我真正愿意每天投入大量时间去研究的事情。

这个决定对我来说非常重要，因为它彻底改变了我的思维方式，也让我拥有了明确的人生方向。在做出这个选择之后，我变得更加自律、更有动力。我开始认真为未来做准备，比如提升英语、坚持编程训练、一步一步学习机器学习。我认为，当一个人拥有清晰目标时，在面对困难时也会更加自信和坚定。

现在回头看，我觉得这个决定不仅塑造了我的学习道路，也塑造了我未来想成为的人。

